-- Panasonic Joins Macerich Building 12 U.S. Solar Power Plants
-- B y   R e e d   L a n d b e r g
-- 2012-10-18T12:28:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-18/panasonic-joins-macerich-building-12-u-s-solar-power-plants.html
A  Panasonic Corp. (6752)  unit said it
joined with  Macerich Co. (MAC)  to build solar power installations at
12 shopping centers in the U.S. in the next year.  The facilities developed by Panasonic Eco Solutions North
America will yeild 10.2 megawatts to 12 megawatts in Arizona,
California, New York and Connecticut, according to a statement
on PRNewswire today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net  